|------|---------|------|-----------|
| `consumer-psychology` | 雙系統思維、聯想記憶、互惠原理、自動化反應、潛意識購買 | Thinking Fast and Slow + Influence + Buyology | `~/.cursor/skills/consumer-psychology/SKILL.md` |
| `influence-seduction` | 九大誘惑角色、間接接近、混合信號、製造需求、暗示植入、懸念、策略性示弱、大眾軟誘惑 | The Art of Seduction (Greene) | `~/.cursor/skills/influence-seduction/SKILL.md` |

